  <brief_title>The Use of Compression Bandages in Total Knee Replacement Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomised Control Trial Investigating the Use of a Two-layer, Short-stretch Compression Bandage in Elective Total Knee Replacement - Feasibility</official_title>
  <sponsors>
